# 📝 To-Do Planner: Flutter App

A beautifully designed **To-Do List & Daily Planner** built using Flutter. This app helps users manage and organize daily tasks efficiently with a clean, professional UI inspired by the **Doist Planner App**.

## 📱 Features

- ✨ Splash screen with animation
- ✅ Add, check, and delete tasks
- 🔔 Reminder if tasks are incomplete
- 🎉 "All tasks completed" success screen
- 🌙 Light & Dark mode support
- 📅 Clean, classic UI with Times New Roman typography

## 🚀 Getting Started

1. **Clone the repository:**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/todo_planner_flutter.git
   cd todo_planner_flutter
   ```

2. **Install dependencies:**
   ```bash
   flutter pub get
   ```

3. **Run the app:**
   ```bash
   flutter run
   ```

> **Note:** Ensure Flutter SDK is installed and properly configured.

## 🗂️ Project Structure

```
lib/
├── main.dart             # Entry point
├── splash_screen.dart    # Splash screen with animation
├── home_screen.dart      # Main task list UI
├── done_screen.dart      # All tasks completed screen
```

## 🎨 UI Design

- Font: **Times New Roman** (classic and readable)
- Icons: Material icons
- Theme: Light theme with soft purple tones and dark mode compatibility

## 📌 Future Enhancements

- Task sync with cloud (Firebase)
- Task time notifications
- Calendar view with schedule planner
